def S2N(m, n):
  return sum(i**j for i in range(m+1) for j in range(n+1))

def S2N(m,n):
    return sum((a**(n+1)-1)//(a-1) if a!=1 else n+1 for a in range(m+1))

def S2N(m,n):
    return sum(base**pow for pow in range(n+1) for base in range(m+1))

def S2N(m, n):
    return sum(b ** e for b in range(m + 1) for e in range(n + 1))

def S2N(m, n):
  return sum(sum(i ** j for i in range(m + 1)) for j in range(n + 1))
